




---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import { Button } from '../components/ui/button';
import { baseUrl } from '../lib/base-url';
---

<MainLayout 
  pageClass=""
  title="About Us | Family-Run Luxury Pet Boarding - Glenugie Kennels, Peterhead"
  description="Learn about Glenugie Kennels - a family-run luxury pet boarding facility in Peterhead, Aberdeenshire. 20+ years experience, 4 exercise areas, themed suites, and exceptional care for your pets."
  keywords="family run kennels Peterhead, pet boarding experience, Glenugie Kennels about, dog boarding Aberdeenshire, professional pet care Scotland"
  ogImage="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f5d3c693d50ca27dfe5a52_PHOTO-2026-05-02-11-29-06.jpg"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-background">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-primary/90 to-primary/80 text-primary-foreground py-24">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-normal text-center mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">About Glenugie Kennels</h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">World-class pet boarding with meticulous care and attention</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Check-in at The Bothy Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
            Check-in at The Bothy
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The reception area in the Bothy is where we meet and greet our VIP's – <strong>Very Important Pooches</strong> or <strong>Pussycats</strong>. We welcome you to get to know everything about your pet.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
              We encourage everyone prior to their stay to complete a form so we can prepare in advance of their arrival.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Scullery Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-muted/30 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
            The Scullery
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center mb-8">
            <div>
              <img 
                src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f3e44190ea19d937ac6a2a_scuillery.png" 
                alt="The Scullery - Glenugie Kennels kitchen" 
                class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
                From pupsicles to pigs ears, fish to fillet steak, our newly refurbished kitchen is packed with the finest cuisine our Very Important Pooches and Very Important Pussycats desire. We are sympathetic to the fact that whilst you're away your pets may refuse their normal diets and it is our promise that we will do our utmost to replenish those appetites.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Our own dogs have thrived on Eukanuba, and we have promoted this food for years, but our pantry is well stocked with various other foods, and, prior to booking, we ask details for all dietary requirements, so we are prepared for their stay with us.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Individual tastes are taken into consideration, and we can cater for those with a more distinguished palate like cooked steak or chicken at an added cost. Should you wish to provide us with your pets specific food this is also not an issue. Medication will be stored and distributed accordingly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fairytails Spa and Grooming Parlour Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 px-4">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
            Fairytails Spa and Grooming Parlour
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-white to-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border-2 border-primary/20">
          <!-- Images Grid -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f303f803359d0a39d8865e_fairytails.png" 
              alt="Fairytails Spa and Grooming Parlour" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
            />
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f303f310c3674e4088c562_fairytails%20products.png" 
              alt="Fairytails grooming products" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Fairytails provides a one stop destination where dogs and cats are pampered by our own daughter, <strong>Savannah</strong> who has a Platinum OCN Diploma in dog grooming and pet first aid. She also has an Introduction to Animal care and NC animal care qualification and has run her own successful grooming business for almost three years.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The salon is fitted with the best equipment to keep your pets fresh and fluffy. With a controlled ambience that allows them as relaxed an atmosphere as possible, it really is a therapeutic place for all visitors.
            </p>
            <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
              From pawdicures and massages to extreme makeovers, blueberry facials to that Hollywood smile, we assure you that your pooch will capture the essence of any admirers at first sniff.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-primary">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">Complimentary Services</h3>
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
                All dogs and cats staying a week or more will receive a complimentary bath and blow-dry but should they wish; any further treatments can be booked prior to their departure through Fairytails booking form.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-primary/20">
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Contact Savannah</p>
                <a href="tel:07727465454" class="text-2xl text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors font-semibold">
                  📞 07727 465454
                </a>
                <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-2">For pricing and appointments</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Fitness Fields Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-muted/30 to-white">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-normal mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary/60 bg-clip-text text-transparent leading-tight">
            Fitness Fields
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Images Grid -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f302baeab20580a95bce31_IMG_1219.jpeg" 
              alt="Fitness Field 1" 
              class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
            />
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f3024595016946a0bd663a_IMG_1658.JPG" 
              alt="Fitness Field 2" 
              class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
            />
            <img 
              src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/69ea97152f20066bc07c2195/69f30400ea27eb32dc703c15_fitness%20fields_.png" 
              alt="Fitness Fields sign" 
              class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl">
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
                We have four fabulous areas situated to the side of the property in which the dogs are free to run wild! Completely enclosed, they are ideal for furry fitness fanatics or docile doggies who just want a stroll. Whatever your pets requirements, you can have peace of mind that they will be safe and secure to the best of our ability whilst staying with us.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border-2 border-primary/20">
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-normal mb-6 text-primary">Hourly Rental Available</h3>
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
              <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Because of the demand for such areas we have also decided to rent them out to anyone on an hourly basis <strong>@£10 per hour</strong> should you wish to use these enclosures for your own dogs. They are 'pawfect' for any dog with behavioural problems, recall etc.
              </p>
              <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Benches are situated beside both areas for your convenience.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border-l-4 border-primary">
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-2">
                  <strong>Important:</strong> It is vital to keep these areas clean and parasite free and so we require that all dogs have been wormed, etc beforehand.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                  Sanitary stations are posted just outside these fields to keep everything spick and span for all our customers.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</MainLayout>





















